                    </p>
                </div>
                <div id="home" style="background-color:#eee; width: 96%; height: 500px; border-radius: 20px; display:flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 20px; flex-direction: column; margin-top: 40px">
                    <h1 style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #00AEC0; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 50px">Your Business Growth</h1>
                    <%= line_chart [
                        { name: "Employee", data: Employee.group_by_day(:created_at).count },
